@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/tasks

### Listar todas as músicas do banco
GET {{baseUrl}}
Accept: application/json


### Buscar música nova -> consultar API
POST {{baseUrl}}/music
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "title": "Yellow",
    "artist": "Coldplay"
}


### Gerar tarefa
POST {{baseUrl}}/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "userId": 10,
    "songId": 1
}

### Enviar resposta
POST {{baseUrl}}/submit
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "taskId": 25,
    "userId": 10,
    "userAnswers": [
        "life",
        "escape",
        "eyes",
        "poor",
        "need",
        "wind",
        "killed",
        "gun",
        "dead",
        "cry",
        "body",
        "die"
    ]
}